  calories: 720 kcal
  fat: 35 g
  saturated fat: 15 g
  carbohydrates: 52 g
  sugar: 7 g
  protein: 49 g
  fiber: 5 g
  sodium: 560 mg
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/mozzarella-herb-chicken-65f1e5cae0c200b440d2cfdf
course: main course
author: HelloFresh
